{
  "title": "Warm Irish Cheese Wrap",
  "description": "A tangy and cheesy Irish dish featuring amaretti and wrapped in a pandan leaf, perfect for a snack or light meal, this whole30 friendly recipe is easy to make and delicious to eat.",
  "cuisine": "Irish",
